data.description:
Beautifully Updated home in the AMAZING LAKES OF CREEKWOOD ADDITION. Come live in this Gorgeous community that is located in Mansfield Award winning schools and offers three private stocked ponds to enjoy. Home is backed up to mature trees with an extended patio and nice covered outdoor living. This split bedroom design home also has a three car garage with in ground basketball hoop. Large room upstairs has full bath and closet that is bedroom or game room layout. New carpet and paint, recently updated kitchen, family room has custom built in entertainment area and a Beautiful Austin Stone fireplace. This home is ready for a new family to come enjoy and partake on living in Mansfield's finest community.
Property HVAC was fully updated 2021
Also extended outdoor living space with covered patio.  With a dog run on the west side of the house.
